Now how is a guy going to be serious and lie? I love him so much and I do want to be serious with him, but he's just always lying and idk it's just to hard to deal with! But anyways I guess I will go and write more in here later to tell you how me n my boyfriend are doing! Brandon babe, if u read this I just want to tell you I love you even if I don't tell you.Okay? Well g2g

Hey Guys,
  Well it's now 10:40 and I'm just writin in my journal again.Well today I went to the movies and then went out to eat at Nachos restraunt! Well since there's not much to say, I'm goin to tell you what happened at the movies! This guy that I don't even know came up behind me and grabbed my a$$ and these are the words he told me,''Hey girl, I'm really diggin ur style and ur lookin pretty fine tonight I love you. Can I have ur name and number?'' Now what kind of stuff is that? Guys if ur readin this never do that to a girl cuz she won't like it. I used think oh I won't care more attention for me but tonight I realized how stupid a guy is when he does that! I mean the guy was cute n all but please come on guys don't be jerks like that!! Well I guess I'm goin to go cuz it's now 10:48 and I'm talking on the fone with my boyfriend!! Luv Ya Guyz!
